Privacy Policy for Sudoku - Brain Puzzle Games

Last updated: March 22, 2026

Ranjith ("we," "our," or "us") built the Sudoku - Brain Puzzle Games app as a free application. This page is used to inform visitors regarding our policies with the collection, use, and disclosure of Personal Information if anyone decided to use our app.

Information Collection and Use

Sudoku - Brain Puzzle Games does not collect, store, transmit, or share any personal information, user data, or usage statistics. The app operates entirely offline and does not require an internet connection to function.

Data Stored Locally on Your Device

The app stores the following data locally on your device only, to provide core functionality:

Game progress (current puzzle state, scores, level completion)
Statistics (games played, win streaks, best times)
Daily challenge history
User preferences (theme, accent color, input mode, difficulty settings)
This data is stored exclusively on your device using local storage and is never transmitted to any external server. If you uninstall the app, all locally stored data is permanently deleted.

Permissions

The app requests the following Android permissions:

VIBRATE — Used to provide haptic feedback during gameplay
POST_NOTIFICATIONS — Used for daily challenge reminders (optional)
No other permissions are requested. The app does not access your camera, microphone, contacts, location, files, or any other sensitive device features.

Third-Party Services

The app does not use any third-party services such as:

Analytics tools (Google Analytics, Firebase Analytics, etc.)
Advertising networks (AdMob, Facebook Ads, etc.)
Crash reporting services
Social media SDKs
Cloud storage or sync services
Children's Privacy

The app does not collect any personal information from anyone, including children under the age of 13. The app contains no ads, no in-app purchases, and no links to external websites, making it safe for users of all ages.

Internet Access

The app does not require or use internet access. It functions entirely offline with no network communication whatsoever.

Data Security

Since no personal data is collected or transmitted, there is no risk of data breach from our end. All game data remains on your device and under your control.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date.

